snippet.title: Calculus: More on Discontinuity
snippet.description:
This video goes through 6 examples of how to identify discontinuities when given the equation of the function.

It is helpful to already have at least a limited background on Discontinuities before watching this video.  

You can watch another one of my videos that introduces Discontinuities at:
https://youtu.be/wUd0SOwxChk
